msgid "Bilinear Interpolation"
msgstr "バイリニア補間"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/deform_brush_engine.rst:75
msgid "Smoothens the result. This causes calculation errors in 16bit."
msgstr "変形結果を滑らかにします。16bitでは計算エラーを起こします。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/deform_brush_engine.rst:77
msgid "Use Counter"
msgstr "カウンターを使う"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/deform_brush_engine.rst:77
msgid "Slows down the deformation subtlety."
msgstr "微妙な変形速度をスローダウンします。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/deform_brush_engine.rst:81
msgid ".. image:: /images/brushes/Krita_deform_brush_useundeformed.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/deform_brush_engine.rst:81
msgid "Without 'use undeformed' to the left and with to the right."
msgstr "左が'変形前を使用'を用いなかった場合で、右が用いた場合です。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/deform_brush_engine.rst:84
msgid ""
"Samples from the previous version of the image instead of the current. This works better with some deform options than others. Move for example seems to almost stop working, but it works really well"
" with Grow."
msgstr "現在の版の代わりに以前の版の画像からサンプルを取ります。いくつかの変形オプションではよく機能します。例えば引き延ばし機能ではほとんど変化が見られませんが、拡大機能では本当によく機能します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/brushes/brush_engines/deform_brush_engine.rst:86
msgid "Use Undeformed Image"
msgstr "変形前の画像を変形のサンプルとして使用"

